IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EUCLIDEAN-DISTANCE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

01 POINT-1.
   05 P1 OCCURS 8 TIMES PIC 9(3)V999 VALUE 0.

01 POINT-2.
   05 P2 OCCURS 8 TIMES PIC 9(3)V999 VALUE 0.

01 I PIC 9 VALUE 1.
01 DIFF PIC S9(5)V999 VALUE 0.
01 SUM-SQUARES PIC 9(8)V999 VALUE 0.
01 DISTANCE PIC ZZZZ9.999 VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.

MAIN-PROCEDURE.

    MOVE 6 TO P1(1)
    MOVE 148 TO P1(2)
    MOVE 72 TO P1(3)
    MOVE 35 TO P1(4)
    MOVE 0 TO P1(5)
    MOVE 33.6 TO P1(6)
    MOVE 0.627 TO P1(7)
    MOVE 50 TO P1(8)

    MOVE 1 TO P2(1)
    MOVE 85 TO P2(2)
    MOVE 66 TO P2(3)
    MOVE 29 TO P2(4)
    MOVE 0 TO P2(5)
    MOVE 26.6 TO P2(6)
    MOVE 0.351 TO P2(7)
    MOVE 31 TO P2(8)

    PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > 8
        COMPUTE DIFF = P1(I) - P2(I)
        COMPUTE SUM-SQUARES = SUM-SQUARES + DIFF * DIFF
    END-PERFORM

    COMPUTE DISTANCE = FUNCTION SQRT(SUM-SQUARES)

    DISPLAY "Euclidean Distance: " DISTANCE

    STOP RUN.